      • XMPPConnector

        public XMPPConnector(String host,
                     String port,
                     String login,
                     String password,
                     String resource)
              throws IllegalArgumentException
        The constructor for the XMPP bot.
        Parameters:
        host - The server the bot should login.
        port - The hosts port.
        login - The bots login name.
        password - The bots login password.
        resource - The bots resource (i.e. Work or Home). Can be null.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - Throws an IllegalArgumentException if some of the parameters are in an invalid format.
